reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great outlet layout - Low profile
reviews.reviewText: Build quality seems decent, and this is a great layout of plugs for what I needed - having multiple plugs in my kitchen on a counter side that had no readily available outlet, *without* surge protection since I have several appliances I needed plugged into it. The small size and orientation of outlets made it much easier to hide it adjacent to my fridge where it would be convenient but hidden from view.
